hidden_village.name: Ayumi
hidden_village.short_lore: Ayumi hails from the Hidden Fox Clan. She is once saved by unknown person who becomes her admired person, she is determined to find this said person.
hidden_village.title: Enigma of the Shadows

hidden_village.short_lore: Centuries ago, in the serene and enchanting forests of the Celestial Plains, the Fox Clan thrived in harmony with nature. The clan members, human-like in appearance but distinguished by their fox ears and tails, lived peacefully under the guidance of their elders and the protection of their ancestral spirits. Among them was a young woman named Petals, known for her beauty, kindness, and strong connection to the natural world.
hidden_village.title: Master of the 6 Pink Petals

hidden_village.short_lore: Aki stands out even among her talented clan, displaying an extraordinary ability to manipulate spirits, much like the legendary Petals.
hidden_village.title: Deity of the Silent Storm
